{"tid":1296232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家多d留意另一網絡輿論戰線","createTime":"2019-07-08T10:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T17:00:51.000Z","uid":626,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5c84c568666689bf64fd19ec2552d2036102a6","tid":1296232,"uid":626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"香港最多人用既IM主要有4個<br />\n<br />\n1.Whatsapp <br />\n2.wechat<br />\n3.tg<br />\n4.Line<br />\n<br />\n其中得line係有新聞既page, 一開line就會見到轉載唔同媒體既報導；<br />\n而係每篇報導下面，係可以俾line user comment,<br />\n我想講既就係呢個位：<br />\n<br />\n由6月尾開始到而家，開始發現越來越多5毛或者深藍account, 一見到示威遊行相關既報導，好快就會留言支持政府同撐警言論；<br />\n一見到示威者或者議員既報導就留言屌，屌完即時又有幾個account like, like數一多就上左熱門，而line default只會show 熱門頭5個comments<br />\n<br />\n本來line就唔算係5毛集中地， 所以我認識既唔少人，包括中立或者淺藍既人士，都會睇留言來揣測民意， 屋企兩老同親戚都會睇line轉載既新聞（因為唔洗downlod其他app, 直接玩im時睇埋，好容易接觸）；早係612至71前，因為未有5毛，就無乜野；<br />\n但71後5毛明顯有組織地係咁洗熱門comments, 灌輸唔正確既message，例如今日議員指控琴日警方行動既新聞：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hypAuyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhypAuyt.png&h=fd30b856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完全係亂咁來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好話唔理呢d地方，我重申line新聞係極易接觸新聞既地方，基本所有用line既人都會見到，隨時比其他地方更快更易接觸新聞，所以灌輸正確訊息俾市民好重要，<br />\n所以我呼籲有用line既朋友，多d like 正確留言，dislike不當留言，以免不當留言成為熱門誤導他人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知有唔少兄弟姊妹做緊，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f9d230246d34d3b9bd31993f1bc6fcd0c93280","tid":1296232,"uid":37990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"另外台仔愛用line!!!<br />\n聯合戰缐！"},{"pid":"a62bedd95dd853b12efb6a60105f4c2bb6b2b26d","tid":1296232,"uid":626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f9d230246d34d3b9bd31993f1bc6fcd0c93280","tid":1296232,"uid":37990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"另外台仔愛用line!!!<br />\n聯合戰缐！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"台仔應該睇唔到香港新聞PAGE既<br />\n主要係想香港既USER 睇到"},{"pid":"cfc54e2bc421bbee5a59e106584d9e04d62baa0f","tid":1296232,"uid":626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1e06173b15f6b37774441b170ba729182903b8","tid":1296232,"uid":626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"推俾多d人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258ea9d4ff1cccd79abc263799e619739d12d157","tid":1296232,"uid":626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"無人用line?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4ee2f02a240e324168f14e7f91519e87b77567","tid":1296232,"uid":68732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:50:01.000Z","msg":"我好少用 幫推"},{"pid":"132b98ff5a423e0b978e331c10dc4d0298f913ed","tid":1296232,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b69a7d1c9fa488a0cb3684344f26ab93d33e2a43","tid":1296232,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f9d230246d34d3b9bd31993f1bc6fcd0c93280","tid":1296232,"uid":37990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"另外台仔愛用line!!!<br />\n聯合戰缐！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:04:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缐</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdbad6724aaaa69b59189fa06c0919e2a3a07f7","tid":1296232,"uid":37990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b69a7d1c9fa488a0cb3684344f26ab93d33e2a43","tid":1296232,"uid":49812,"like":0,"